                       <h4 class="service-heading"><strong>Psychotherapy</strong></h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">Our therapeutic approach is eclectic, based on psychodynamic, Humanistic, Cognitive and Behaviorial theories and Positive Psychology according to our appreciation of the situation in presence.</p>

